posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 715 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to Cambridge Towers Apartments in Hopkins, Minnesota!', 'Cambridge Towers offers studio, one bedroom and two bedroom units in a 7 story building.', 'Enjoy a modern fitness center, an internet lounge with free internet and printer services, and a large outdoor patio for picnics and barbecues.', 'Having friends or family over for the evening?', 'Host a party in our fully equipped party room.', 'Most apartment units also feature a generously sized balcony with a west or east view.', "Conveniently located on Highway 7 across from The Shoppes at Knollwood, you'll be close to shopping, grocery stores, and restaurants.", 'The newly renovated Cottageville Park with its trails, lighting and a permanent community garden is just a block from your front door.', 'Call today to schedule your personal tour!', 'Features:', 'Refrigerator, Patio/Balcony, Disposal, Dishwasher, Air Conditioner, Range, Cable Ready', 'Community Amenities:', 'Controlled Access/Gated, Elevator, Free Weights, Community Room, On-Site Management, Garage, Internet Lounge, On-Site Maintenance, Laundry Facilities, Fitness Center', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'ZTPx81MvAv']
